  examples: '<p><span class="red">Incorrect: This is <b>waste</b> of time!</span><br/><span class="green">Correct: This is <b>a waste</b> of time!</span><br/><p><span class="red">Incorrect: I want to take a tour of <b>art museum</b>.</span><br/><span class="green">Correct: I want to take a tour of <b>the art museum</b>.</span><br/>',
